ution holding a valid sponsor licence. Requires Confirmation of Acceptance for Studies (CAS) and online UKVI application."},{"q":"What is Eligible applicants for this service?","a":"Valid CAS · Proof of funds · English at required level · Genuine student intent · TB test if from listed country"},{"q":"What is Financial requirement for this service?","a":"Tuition minus deposit paid + living costs (London vs outside London rates). 28-day funds rule applies."},{"q":"Important note on Financial requirement?","a":"Tuition minus deposit paid + living costs (London vs outside London rates). 28-day funds rule applies."},{"q":"What is Key authority for this service?","a":"UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) — Home Office"},{"q":"What is After approval for this service?","a":"BRP or digital status; maintain attendance, sponsor reporting, and work hour limits."},{"q":"Is CAS from licensed UK sponsor required?","a":"CAS number valid and unused"},{"q":"Is Financial requirement met (28-day rule) required?","a":"Funds held 28 consecutive days"},{"q":"Is English language at SELT level (if required) required?","a":"IELTS UKVI or exempt pathway"},{"q":"Is TB test certificate (if applicable) required?","a":"Required for Indian nationals"},{"q":"Is ATAS certificate (if course requires) required?","a":"Check CAS and course code"},{"q":"Is Genuine student / credible study plan required?","a":"Genuine student / credible study plan is typically required."},{"q":"Is Immigration history disclosed required?","a":"Immigration history disclosed is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"3–8w — Outside UK standard"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"£524 — + IHS per year of course"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"89% — ~76% industry benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"13 — + financial evidence"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & IHS"},{"q":"What if the client has 28-day funds rule breach?","a":"Maintain required ba